name: Super Snack Time
description:
Made for Ludum Dare 33 with the theme "You are the monster"

How to play:
ASD to attack.
Don't let your plants go hungry, they will wither and die.
If too many of your snacks get past it's game over.

See if you can beat my high score of 2930!
It gets crazy around 1000...
